title.narrative: ICT - T4D:OPERATIONAL EFFECTIVENESS

description.narrative: Country Office has a resilient ICT infrastructure and services to conduct Programme and Operations delivery. Optimized innovative solutions are also deployed to increase Programme and Operations efficiencies, while supporting real-time Programme monitoring, which contributes to Operations Support To Programme Delivery. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Operational Support To Programme Delivery. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: The Country Office programmes have management and operations practices that are cost-effective, efficient, secured and risk- informed.

description.narrative: ICT team was able to improve connectivity of all offices by migrating to much faster ISPs, while reducing the annual cost by 50%. ICT also have migrated all office data to the cloud to facilitate tele-working and improve data availability. With two applications already operational, R&R and Juba Trips, ICT were able to improve the efficiency of two common and time-consuming processes, saving staff time, and increasing efficiency.; | Status:On-track | As-of Date:11/01/2022
